OL,3,C'She was my best friend and you killed
OL,4,Cher,' witness tells murder accused
OL,6,FA former partner of Natalie McNally
OL,7,Fhas described how she was his best
OL,8,Ffriend and accused Stephen McCullagh
OL,9,Fof murdering her.
OL,11,FHe looked towards the dock, in front
OL,12,Fof Ms McNally's family and friends in
OL,13,Fthe public gallery, and said: "She was
OL,14,Fmy best friend and you killed her".
OL,16,FIt came during the third week of the
OL,17,Ftrial of Stephen McCullagh for the
OL,18,Fmurder of Ms McNally, who had been 15
OL,19,Fweeks pregnant with his child.
OL,26,@uD@_OUvD@bO]
