OL,3,C'She was my best friend and you killed
OL,4,Cher,' witness tells murder accused
OL,6,FMcCullagh, 36, of Woodland Gardens in
OL,7,FLisburn, has pleaded not guilty to the
OL,8,Fmurder charge against him at Belfast
OL,9,FCrown Court.
OL,11,FThe trial previously heard McCullagh
OL,12,Fhad claimed that Ms McNally's ex had
OL,13,Fbeen responsible for her murder.
OL,15,FA jury of six men and six women has
OL,16,Fbeen sworn in to serve during the
OL,17,Ftrial, which is expected to last
OL,18,Faround five weeks, before Mr Justice
OL,19,FPatrick Kinney.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
