OL,3,C'She was my best friend and you killed
OL,4,Cher,' witness tells murder accused
OL,6,FThe former partner of Ms McNally, who
OL,7,Fcannot be named because of a court
OL,8,Forder, had been in a relationship with
OL,9,FMs McNally from 2019.
OL,11,FDespite the pair both becoming
OL,12,Finvolved with new partners, they had
OL,13,Fcontinued to message on and off, and
OL,14,Falso had met up to have sex, including
OL,15,Fin October 2022.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
