PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1773173478
OL,3,C'She was my best friend and you killed
OL,4,Cher,' witness tells murder accused
OL,6,FThe court heard the content of
OL,7,Fexchanges between them via email and
OL,8,FWhatsApp messages which included
OL,9,Farguments about their relationship, Ms
OL,10,FMcNally's dog and cat, family issues
OL,11,Fher ex had been having and McCullagh.
OL,13,FExchanges of sexual messages,
OL,14,Fincluding multiple requests to meet up
OL,15,Ffor sex by him were also read.
OL,17,FThe court also heard that McCullagh
OL,18,Fhad the password to open Ms McNally's
OL,19,Fphone.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
