OL,3,C'She was my best friend and you killed
OL,4,Cher,' witness tells murder accused
OL,6,FAppearing in court, the man said he
OL,7,Finitially met Ms McNally on the dating
OL,8,Fapp Tinder in 2019, and moved into her
OL,9,Fhouse.
OL,11,FWhile he moved out in 2020 after being
OL,12,Foffered a Housing Executive flat, the
OL,13,Fman said they continued to meet up.
OL,15,F"Natalie was my best friend, and the
OL,16,Frelationship never ended to be honest
OL,17,Fas far as friends went," he said, but
OL,18,Fsaid he got together with his current
OL,19,Fpartner in 2022.
