OL,3,C'She was my best friend and you killed
OL,4,Cher,' witness tells murder accused
OL,6,F"I was trying to be good, but I kept
OL,7,Fin touch with Natalie."
OL,9,FHe said the last time he met up with
OL,10,FMs McNally for a physical encounter
OL,11,Fwas at her home in Lurgan in October
OL,12,F2022, and said his last memory of her
OL,13,Fwas feeling that she was annoyed both
OL,14,Fat him and herself.
OL,16,F"The last time I saw Natalie, she was
OL,17,Flying on her bed on her side, I could
OL,18,Ftell she was raging at me, we'd had
OL,19,Fsex, and then I was away...
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@WO]xD@AOU
