OL,3,C'She was my best friend and you killed
OL,4,Cher,' witness tells murder accused
OL,6,F"That memory of the last time seeing
OL,7,Fher, I really wish it was something
OL,8,Fnicer than her looking annoyed at me,
OL,9,Fannoyed at herself even I think," he
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"I'm not proud of it, I'm not proud of
OL,13,Fany of these text messages.
OL,15,F"I definitely took advantage of
OL,16,FNatalie, I feel horrible about it."
OL,18,FHe went on: "Natalie really was my
OL,19,Fbest friend", and looking towards the
OL,20,Fdock, "and you killed her".
