OL,3,C'She was my best friend and you killed
OL,4,Cher,' witness tells murder accused
OL,6,FAsked for his thoughts about how he
OL,7,Ftreated Ms McNally, the man said the
OL,8,Fmessages "don't paint a very good
OL,9,Fpicture of me".
OL,11,F"There was a lot more to me and
OL,12,FNatalie's relationship than these text
OL,13,Fmessages, I knew her for four years,
OL,14,Fshe was my best friend," he said.
OL,16,F"She was the nicest girl ever, she
OL,17,Fwould have done anything for anybody,
OL,18,Fshe helped me in so much and I feel
OL,19,Fhorrible...
