OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1773173478
OL,3,C'She was my best friend and you killed
OL,4,Cher,' witness tells murder accused
OL,6,F"I just wish I had been better to her
OL,7,Fbecause I definitely took advantage of
OL,8,FNatalie and her good heart."
OL,10,FThe man said he was initially
OL,11,Fapproached by police to give a
OL,12,Fstatement following Ms McNally's
OL,13,Fmurder, and was later arrested.
OL,15,F"I wanted to help as much as possible,
OL,16,FI knew I hadn't done it so I had
OL,17,Fnothing to worry about... when it was
OL,18,Fexplained I was under arrest, my jaw
OL,19,Fdropped, 'are you serious, I'll go
OL,20,Fwith you and help, but the truth will
OL,21,Falways come out'," he said.
